flowchart TD
    A{What do you know about the data?} -->|Number of clusters known| B[K-Means]
    A -->|Unknown clusters, no noise assumption| C[Hierarchical]
    A -->|Arbitrary shapes, noise expected| D[DBSCAN]
    A -->|Need probability of membership| E[Gaussian Mixture]

    B --> B1["Fast, scalable Assumes spherical clusters Sensitive to k choice"]
    C --> C1["No k needed upfront Dendrogram shows structure Slower on large data"]
    D --> D1["Finds outliers naturally Handles odd shapes Needs ε and minPts tuning"]
    E --> E1["Soft assignments More flexible shapes Expectation-Maximization"]
